        <p style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);font-size:13px;margin-top:6px;">
          What makes humans irreplaceable when AI can do almost anything?
        </p>
        <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-top:4px;">2026-05-07</p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom:var(--spacing-lg);border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border);padding-bottom:var(--spacing-sm);">
        <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-bottom:var(--spacing-xs);">May 2026</p>
        <div style="padding:var(--spacing-md) 0;">
          <span style="background:rgba(201,169,110,0.1);color:var(--color-accent-dark);padding:2px 8px;border-radius:12px;font-size:11px;">Human-AI Fit</span>
          <span style="background:rgba(15,43,70,0.05);color:var(--color-text-secondary);padding:2px 8px;border-radius:12px;font-size:11px;margin-left:6px;">AI Education</span>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-size:1rem;line-height:1.4;"><a href="/en/blog/ai_knowledge_meaning/" style="color:var(--color-primary);text-decoration:none;">Does Learning Still Matter in the Age of AI?</a></h3>
        <p style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);font-size:13px;margin-top:6px;">
          Why personal knowledge still matters when every answer is just a query away.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-top:4px;">2026-05-07</p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom:var(--spacing-lg);border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border);padding-bottom:var(--spacing-sm);">
        <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-bottom:var(--spacing-xs);">May 2026</p>
        <div style="padding:var(--spacing-md) 0;">
          <span style="background:rgba(201,169,110,0.1);color:var(--color-accent-dark);padding:2px 8px;border-radius:12px;font-size:11px;">Policy Analysis</span>
