        <div style="padding:var(--spacing-md) 0;">
          <span style="background:rgba(201,169,110,0.1);color:var(--color-accent-dark);padding:2px 8px;border-radius:12px;font-size:11px;">Policy Analysis</span>
          <span style="background:rgba(15,43,70,0.05);color:var(--color-text-secondary);padding:2px 8px;border-radius:12px;font-size:11px;margin-left:6px;">IRA & Climate</span>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-size:1rem;line-height:1.4;"><a href="/en/blog/us_policy_table_2026/" style="color:var(--color-primary);text-decoration:none;">US EV Policy: Boom, Bust, and the IRA's Unfinished Revolution</a></h3>
        <p style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);font-size:13px;margin-top:6px;">
          61 policies from ARRA to the second Trump rollback (2009–2026).
        </p>
        <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-top:4px;">2026-05-04</p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom:var(--spacing-lg);border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border);padding-bottom:var(--spacing-sm);">
        <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-bottom:var(--spacing-xs);">May 2026</p>
        <div style="padding:var(--spacing-md) 0;">
          <span style="background:rgba(201,169,110,0.1);color:var(--color-accent-dark);padding:2px 8px;border-radius:12px;font-size:11px;">Company News</span>
          <span style="background:rgba(15,43,70,0.05);color:var(--color-text-secondary);padding:2px 8px;border-radius:12px;font-size:11px;margin-left:6px;">Human-AI Fit</span>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-size:1rem;line-height:1.4;"><a href="/en/blog/about_humanaifit/" style="color:var(--color-primary);text-decoration:none;">Meet humanaifit — Where Humans and AI Actually Work Together</a></h3>
        <p style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);font-size:13px;margin-top:6px;">
          Introducing Beacon Consulting — a new advisory firm grounded in Human-AI Fit research.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-top:4px;">2026-05-03</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-dark text-center">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Want to work with us?</h2>
      <p style="max-width:500px;margin:var(--spacing-md) auto var(--spacing-xl);opacity:0.85;font-size:15px;">
        Whether you want to improve your team's AI effectiveness or prepare for CBAM compliance, we're here to help.
      </p>
      <a href="/en/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">Get in Touch →</a>
    </div>
